To the Knowledge of the Manager, no plan described on Schedule I is subject to any ongoing audit, investigation or other administrative proceeding of any Governmental Authority nor has any Action been commenced against any such plan (other than for benefits in the ordinary course), in which the adverse result thereof would result in a Material Adverse Effect on the Railcars and the Leases, or on the Company after the Closing Date.
