Item 2.03 Creation of a Direct Financial Obligation or an Obligation under an Off-Balance Sheet Arrangement of a Registrant.
On March 27, 2008, The Andersons, Inc. (the "Company"), entered into a Note Purchase Agreement with several purchasers under which the Company will receive $195.0 million in three series of Senior Guaranteed Notes. Wells Fargo Capital Markets acted as Agent. The foregoing description of the Agreement does not purport to be complete and is qualified in its entirety by reference to the Agreement which is filed as exhibit 10.29.
Top of the Form
