Following a Qualifying Termination other than in connection with a Change in Control, your benefit period for purposes of the cash severance and other benefits described in Sections 5, and 6 of the Policy shall be one (1) year (Company Staff)the longer of (a) or (b) where (a) equals 6 months and (b) equals 3 weeks per year of service up to a maximum of 52 weeks (other Participants).
