"" means any Indebtedness borrowed, raised or incurred by the Company or any of its Subsidiaries with respect to the financing of Rail Assets, in respect of which (i) recourse of the limited recourse financiers is limited to such Rail Assets, (ii) there is no recourse whatsoever, directly or indirectly (including by way of Guaranty, set-off, subrogation, execution or specific performance), to, or in respect of, the Company or any Subsidiary, and (iii) no limited recourse financier can seek to wind up or place in administration or make or pursue any claim in the winding up or administration of the Company or any Subsidiary (or any similar or equivalent action under the laws of any relevant jurisdiction), subject to, in each of the preceding cases, Limited Recourse Exceptions.
