Restricted Payment
provided
Except for (a) advances for travel and expenses to their officers, directors, managers, general partners or employees in the ordinary course of their business, and (b) as permitted by Section 8.8, Borrower and its consolidated subsidiaries shall not make advances or loans in or to any Affiliates. All transactions with Affiliates shall be bona fide arms length transactions that are no less favorable to Borrower and its consolidated subsidiaries than would be a similar transaction with a non-affiliated third person.
