ents and (vii) the Lender assignor thereunder shall be deemed to have relinquished its rights and to be released from its obligations under the Financing Agreements, to the extent (and only to the extent) that its rights and obligations hereunder have been assigned by it pursuant to such Assignment and Acceptance (and, in the case of an Assignment and Acceptance covering all or the remaining portion of an assigning Lender's rights and obligations under the Financing Agreements, such Lender shall cease to be a party thereto).
