Waiver of Demand
.
Upon the occurrence and during the continuance of any Matured Default, Borrower waives, to the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, all rights to notice and hearing of any kind prior to the exercise by the Agent of the Agent's rights.
9.4
Waiver of Notice
