SELLER is engaged in the ownership and operation of 12 grain handling and storage, agronomy, plant nutrient and fuel distribution facilities (each, a Facility and collectively, the Facilities) having an aggregate grain storage capacity of 36,032,000 bushels and located in the states of Iowa, and Tennessee, and listed, together with the individual SELLER owning such Facility on
