(i)
SELLER has good, valid and legal title in and to each parcel of real property constituting the Facilities, free and clear of all Liens other than Permitted Liens. Great Lakes has good, valid and legal title in and to each parcel of real property constituting the Facilities owned by it, free and clear of all Liens other than Permitted Liens.
